g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f62ad22f49fdbfe57c7911dcf16454b68d7add","tid":1530281,"uid":142803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:21:06.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n2:30 添馬"},{"pid":"40c8d55202f04c70c4447fd80d1f0a8578c44296","tid":1530281,"uid":159596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:41:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c73c229cde4195257951ec3cb087acce74df0da8","tid":1530281,"uid":2207,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"唔係話笑你, 同分化<br />\n不過你做得2 間學校, 仲要TA<br />\n你真係識條春咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次EDB 就事件已經有哂指引點做<br />\n好取決於校長係咩立場同埋佢要點處理<br />\n<br />\n你根本識既野, 同知道既野太少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸: 做過7間學校, 亦仲係教畜"},{"pid":"555089c9bec150c5622eb46bd75fc92b72845d44","tid":1530281,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c73c229cde4195257951ec3cb087acce74df0da8","tid":1530281,"uid":2207,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"唔係話笑你, 同分化<br />\n不過你做得2 間學校, 仲要TA<br />\n你真係識條春咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次EDB 就事件已經有哂指引點做<br />\n好取決於校長係咩立場同埋佢要點處理<br />\n<br />\n你根本識既野, 同知道既野太少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸: 做過7間學校, 亦仲係教畜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:13:03.000Z","msg":"學校通過家教會做好多嘢，唔係靠媒體。面對社區，唔係全香港。<br />\n利伸: 做過 SGM。"},{"pid":"9e69c9e3a22f647436017f23679bbc5e76a507db","tid":1530281,"uid":2207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:22:12.000Z","msg":"以一個教畜身份同大家講<br />\n<br />\n要學生無事<br />\n就一定要多人參與<br />\n學校可以靠嚇記全班30個大過<br />\n不過當你全校1000個學生參與, 佢就無得咁做。<br />\n當你每間學校都幾百人參與, 你唔帶口罩, 甚至唔著褲都無問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人數從來都係最重要因素。"},{"pid":"b59296c7a296c874e917c059b68f92eac8cea8ba","tid":1530281,"uid":152061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c73c229cde4195257951ec3cb087acce74df0da8","tid":1530281,"uid":2207,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"唔係話笑你, 同分化<br />\n不過你做得2 間學校, 仲要TA<br />\n你真係識條春咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次EDB 就事件已經有哂指引點做<br />\n好取決於校長係咩立場同埋佢要點處理<br />\n<br />\n你根本識既野, 同知道既野太少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸: 做過7間學校, 亦仲係教畜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:34:38.000Z","msg":"唔係話教畜就係咩，但教畜都知道一間學校賤起上黎TA都要做埋IC嗰份，家教選舉同IMC開會都要跟上司列席落記錄時，訓導都有份玩埋既時候，TA會唔知入面d野點玩？<br />\n而家要既就係用輿論踢爆學校d陰質野，特別係染紅既學校、扮晒有外藉學生就以為係國際學校嗰d，高層永遠大事化無小事就屈人做，唔踢爆d衰野比佢地知有人mon住佢地做野係唔係想比機會d警二代繼續作威作福？<br />\n學校高層要掩飾d衰野，可以令受害者被施害者，同黑警一樣<br />\n<br />\n利申：其中一間係港島最南有航海科讀既學校"},{"pid":"dc312e06e8df69538724993e8b957afaaf9990a2","tid":1530281,"uid":117232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:37:59.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776c8dc8f91d3041ec7a90afd00a5ecfba424f87","tid":1530281,"uid":2207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b59296c7a296c874e917c059b68f92eac8cea8ba","tid":1530281,"uid":152061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c73c229cde4195257951ec3cb087acce74df0da8","tid":1530281,"uid":2207,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"唔係話笑你, 同分化<br />\n不過你做得2 間學校, 仲要TA<br />\n你真係識條春咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次EDB 就事件已經有哂指引點做<br />\n好取決於校長係咩立場同埋佢要點處理<br />\n<br />\n你根本識既野, 同知道既野太少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸: 做過7間學校, 亦仲係教畜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:34:38.000Z","msg":"唔係話教畜就係咩，但教畜都知道一間學校賤起上黎TA都要做埋IC嗰份，家教選舉同IMC開會都要跟上司列席落記錄時，訓導都有份玩埋既時候，TA會唔知入面d野點玩？<br />\n而家要既就係用輿論踢爆學校d陰質野，特別係染紅既學校、扮晒有外藉學生就以為係國際學校嗰d，高層永遠大事化無小事就屈人做，唔踢爆d衰野比佢地知有人mon住佢地做野係唔係想比機會d警二代繼續作威作福？<br />\n學校高層要掩飾d衰野，可以令受害者被施害者，同黑警一樣<br />\n<br />\n利申：其中一間係港島最南有航海科讀既學校"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:45:22.000Z","msg":"你要摸清每間校長係咩立場。<br />\n<br />\n如果校長同大家同一陣線, 佢比一定自由度學生, 成件事會容易好多<br />\n如果校長同大家對立, 佢就會搞大, 甚至唔理學校已有形象, 報警/ 上EDB<br />\n<br />\n所以我重申<br />\n你踢爆「陰質野」呢d 唔係而家做,<br />\n而家要每間學校要有足夠人數去行動&amp;自我保護。<br />\n<br />\n我認為無200人以上, 就會好危險。"},{"pid":"41e6be0e8f8e38a27d1fa96b3ed0701e3e351711","tid":1530281,"uid":12440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}